                            <p>Building community and support networks</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Us Section -->
        <section id="about" class="py-16 bg-green">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-olive">About Us</h2>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-12">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Our Founding Story</h3>
                        <p class="text-lg mb-6">Hayden's Hub was founded in 2022 by a group of parents and caregivers who recognized the need for better support systems for youth with special needs in Ottawa. After experiencing firsthand the challenges of navigating resources and services, they came together to create a centralized hub of information and community support.</p>
                        <p class="text-lg">Named after Hayden, a young person whose journey inspired our founders, our organization has grown into a vital resource for families across the Ottawa region.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Our Mission</h3>
