                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Our Vision</h3>
                            <p class="text-lg">A community where all youth with special needs have equal opportunities to thrive, connect, and access the support they need to reach their full potential.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
